{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9e4c85bea2","title":"对总政关于西南军区三反运动第三周简报的批示的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19091131db","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":15,"articleId":"9e4c85bea2"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"de0fbd4e1e","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"肖华，当时任人民革命军事委员会总政治部副主任。"},{"id":"9926bb634b","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指军委总政治部1952年1月14日对西南军区三反第三周简报的批示。批示指出：对于资污行为和一般公私不分的错误行为，必须加以区分，并分别对待，不能把占公家的小便宜统统叫作资污：简报说不少单位是百分之百的人员有大小不同的贪污行为，这样把贫污面扩大到所有人员身上，会减低反贫污斗争的严重意义，转移对真正大贫污犯的斗争火力，领导上将陷于被动，对群众也没有教育意义。"},{"id":"2ca531805a","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指毛泽东1952年1月15日对西南军区党委关于三反运动情况简报的批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"79f3cfc172","type":"title","text":"对总政关于西南军区三反运动第三周简报的批示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2"},{"id":"de0fbd4e1e","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2"},{"id":"9926bb634b","type":"paragraph","text":"这个指示不妥，不要发出。西南军区后勤系统清出百分之三十四的贫污分子是合乎事实的。自前的大多数机关部队的偏向是不愿或不知道认真去清查贪污分子。我对西南一月十二日的报告已另有批示。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2"},{"id":"2ca531805a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2"},{"id":"4570b26192","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2"}],"page":{"id":"d30f5597a1","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"9e4c85bea2","start":274,"end":274}}}},"__N_SSG":true}